NG0438:0: @#/  / rin po che shes rab kyi rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0438:1: lnga phung yan lag thams cad ni //
NG0438:2: 'bru lnga bzhag pa'i byang chub ste //
NG0438:3: om dang sku 'drar 'brel bas byang chub nyid las byung //
NG0438:4: spyi ni brjod pas thams cad ming tsam yin te a //
NG0438:5: a nyid mngon rdzogs rgyal po dbyings kyi ngang //
NG0438:6: skye 'jig nyid na yi ge a //
NG0438:7: de nyid byang chub sems yin te //
NG0438:8: mi dmigs byang chub mchog 'byung ba'i //
NG0438:10: zad med rin chen gter yin te //
NG0438:11: mngon shes drug ldan mtshan gsol dpags //
NG0438:12: de nyid phung po rdzogs pa'i don //
NG0438:13: gnyis med ye shes byang chub sems //
NG0438:14: mi dmigs ye shes thig ler gsal //
NG0438:15: spros med ye shes nam mkha'i dbyings //
NG0438:16: 'gyur med ye shes rgyas pa la //
NG0438:17: rgyas 'debs chen po bdag nyid che //
NG0438:18: a ho phyogs bcu rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun //
NG0438:19: des pa'i don bkrol bzhi bcu rtsalngar gsungs //
NG0438:20: bsdus pa'i don du ye shes 'bru lngar gsungs //
NG0438:21: lnga po nyid kyang 'bru gsum nang du bsdus //
NG0438:22: gsum po nyid kyang yi ge ar 'dus te //
NG0438:23: a nyid ma skyes mngon rdzogs nyid la thim //
NG0438:24: dbyings nyid ye nas rin chen lus la gsal //
NG0438:25: rin chen lus nyid ye shes bcud la @#//
NG0438:27: hum ni bde chen thugs kyi dbyings //
NG0438:28: skye 'gag med pa'i g.yung drung dbyings //
NG0438:29: gang gis rtogs pa rin po che //
NG0438:30: rdo rje spu gri gnon po ste //
NG0438:31: gsang chen bde ba'i thig btab pas //
NG0438:32: ma gos lam zhes bgrod du med //
NG0438:33: de nyid dur khrod dpal chen te //
NG0438:34: thugs ni he chen dpal gyi ngo bor bstan //
NG0438:35: om badzra shri he ru ka hum //
NG0438:36: dbyings dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0438:37: a la spros shing bsdu ba ni //
NG0438:38: gsang ba'i thig le nyid kyi dbyings //
NG0438:39: nam mkha'i dbyings nas sprin byung ste //
NG0438:40: sa las 'bras bu sna tshogs smin //
NG0438:41: gcig pu'i ngang las bsam mi khyab //
NG0438:42: byin rlabs yon tan chen po 'byung //
NG0438:43: yon tan rin chen 'byung ldan che ho //
NG0438:44: gcig gi ngang las bsam mi khyab //
NG0438:45: dbyings las mi zhan yon tan thig le'i ngang //
NG0438:46: ye nas dbyings nyid che ba'i tshul //
NG0438:47: snang byed nyid la bya byed med par gnas //
NG0438:48: ye shes brdal khyab rin po che //
NG0438:49: phyi mar gar 'gro bstan pa ni //
NG0438:50: rnam shes sems kyi rgyal po la //
NG0438:51: ting 'dzin thugs la byin gyis brlabs //
NG0438:52: mi skyes sems kyi me long la //
NG0438:53: mi 'gog sku yi ngo bor gsal //
NG0438:54: skye 'gag med pa'i chos dbyings las //
NG0438:55: bde ba chen po'i 'od zer gsal //
NG0438:56: de yi ngang las nges pa'i don //
NG0438:57: mngon rdzogs rgyal po'i dbyings la rol //
NG0438:58: bde chen rgyal ba'i thugs la shar //
NG0438:59: rin chen sprul pa spros pas khams gsum dbyings la rol //
NG0438:60: chags med thugs la shar bas srid pa'i dpa' bo mdzad //
NG0438:61: rtsa brgyad lus la rdzogs pas dpag tsam sku yi brgyan //
NG0438:62: thig le dbyings la sbyor bas nyes pa'i skyon mi mnga' //
NG0438:63: shes rab mchog dang rnam bral ba //
NG0438:64: dug dang 'khor ba mthong ba yi //
NG0438:65: rang sems bslus pa'i sems can la //
NG0438:66: nam yang spel bar yong ma gsungs //
